            <section ID="ID_bf89af8d-9852-4bcd-8ae9-f18199209c9e">
               <id root="52207853-4446-f142-e063-6394a90a281c"/>
               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>1 INDICATIONS AND USAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>ZIRGAN is indicated for the treatment of acute herpetic keratitis (dendritic ulcers) in adults and pediatric patients aged 2 years and older.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20260101"/>
               <excerpt>
                  <highlight>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>ZIRGAN is a nucleoside analog antiviral indicated for the treatment of acute herpetic keratitis (dendritic ulcers) in adults and pediatric patients aged 2 years and older. (
 
    <linkHtml href="#ID_bf89af8d-9852-4bcd-8ae9-f18199209c9e">1</linkHtml>)

   </paragraph>
                     </text>
                  </highlight>
               </excerpt>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="ID_95e2dd95-7625-440d-a0ae-542ac8a5c749">
               <id root="52207853-4447-f142-e063-6394a90a281c"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>2 DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>The recommended dosage is 1 drop in the affected eye 5 times per day (approximately every 3 hours while awake) until the corneal ulcer heals, and then 1 drop 3 times per day for 7 days.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20260101"/>
               <excerpt>
                  <highlight>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Apply 1 drop in the affected eye 5 times per day (approximately every 3 hours while awake) until the corneal ulcer heals, and then 1 drop 3 times per day for 7 days. (
 
    <linkHtml href="#ID_95e2dd95-7625-440d-a0ae-542ac8a5c749">2</linkHtml>)

   </paragraph>
                     </text>
                  </highlight>
               </excerpt>
            </section>
         </component>
